,Recommended,312210,12748322,"Posted: 2 November, 2014",all,Kobe Leonard,"A great idea for a game and its looking really promising so far. Can't wait to see the finished product, sadly though updates have been slow. Theres a small dev team for the game so I dont see it being complete anytime soon or at all honestly.The game is about robots and right now there are three types, drones, suicidal bombers that wiggle like weird ♥♥♥♥ers, and a regular one with a gun. They all hunt you down but drones only go after you if you get too close. The point of the game seems to be to hack stuff and build a base. You have to scavenge for things like weapons, building manuals, hack tools, and some other neat stuff then survive. The tutorial covers everything so Im not going to.The only way to have fun is to play one of the few multiplayer modes or try and survive with a friend. When I first bought this game about a year ago or more, I found exploring the open world fun, but that didnt last long. I kept getting spooked by the hunters and♥♥♥♥♥♥and eventually I explored everything, so I guess you can explore at first but I recommend multiplayer."
